1. *Pojavila* se nova zvezda na muzičkoj sceni. (A new star appeared on the music scene.)
2. Ona se *pojavila* i razbudila sve u sobi. (She appeared and woke everyone up in the room.)
3. U njegovom životu se *pojavila* nova ljubav. (A new love appeared in his life.)
4. Svi su gledali kako se nad gradom *pojavila* nova planeta. (Everyone watched as a new planet appeared over the city.)
5. On se *pojavio* u tom trenutku kada je najviše bila potrebna pomoć. (He appeared at that moment when help was most needed.)
6. Na obzoru se *pojavila* zvezda. (A star appeared on the horizon.)